text: The 2019 Engie Open de Seine-et-Marne was a professional tennis tournament played on indoor hard courts. It was the seventh edition of the tournament which was part of the 2019 ITF Women's World Tennis Tour. It took place in Croissy-Beaubourg, France between 25 and 31 March 2019. ==Singles main draw entrants== ===Seeds=== {|class="sortable wikitable" |- ! width="70"| Country ! width="175"| Player !
